Complex C# library for Firebase Realtime Database built on top of Firebase REST API. Among others it supports following:

      * Offline storage
      * Querying using available filters
      * Passing in authentication token
      * Streaming online changes
      * Directly Posting / Putting / Patching online data

      Streaming changes (both online and offline) are done using Reactive Extensions.

Suitest instrumentation library for Xbox apps.

This package will make your Xbox app testable with Suitest. Suitest is a multi-platform end-to-end test automation service with the focus on the productivity and ease of use. Sign up for free at https://suite.st to get started.

To prepare your Xbox app for end-to-end testing with Suitest:

1. Add this package to your Xbox app dependencies.
2. In Package.appxmanifest add "Internet (Client)" capability.
3. Call SuitestLibrary.Suitest.Initialize(); near the end of your OnLaunched method in App.xaml.cs.

Then upload the instrumented Xbox app package into Suitest and test away!

Happy testing!
summary: Suitest instrumentation library for Xbox apps.
